👤 About Me

I am YuvaSri M, a Software Developer with 2 years of experience in React and Python development. I specialize in building dynamic, responsive UI components, integrating backend services, and delivering AI-based intelligent solutions. My focus is on performance optimization, scalability, and user-centric design.

🔹 Key Skills

