Tools: Git, Jira

🔹 Practical Scenarios
React Scenario – Performance Optimization

Challenge: A dashboard built with React and ApexCharts was slowing down due to frequent re-renders and heavy data processing.
Action:

Used React.memo and useCallback to reduce unnecessary re-renders.

Implemented virtualized lists for large data sets.

Optimized API calls with debouncing and caching.
Result: Improved rendering speed by 40%, resulting in smoother UI and better user experience.

Python Scenario – AI-Powered Query System

Challenge: Users struggled with writing SQL queries for a PostgreSQL database.
Action:

Built an LLM-powered AI agent that converts natural language queries into SQL.

Integrated error handling and schema validation for reliable results.

Used Python + FastAPI for backend and exposed endpoints to frontend.
Result: Reduced manual query writing efforts by 70% and empowered non-technical users to fetch insights easily.

