Q2. What is your greatest strength?
My greatest strength is my problem-solving mindset. I don’t just write code; I analyze the root cause, implement efficient solutions, and always focus on long-term maintainability.

Q3. What is your greatest weakness?
Earlier, I used to dive deep into details, which sometimes slowed delivery. I’ve worked on improving this by balancing quality with timelines, ensuring I deliver reliable solutions without unnecessary delays.

Q4. How do you handle pressure or tight deadlines?
I prioritize tasks based on impact and urgency, break them into smaller milestones, and communicate progress regularly. This helps me stay focused and ensures timely delivery without compromising quality.

Q5. Why should we hire you?
You should hire me because I bring a blend of technical expertise in React & Python, hands-on AI solution development, and a strong focus on user experience. I can contribute not only by writing efficient code but also by driving innovation and scalability in your projects.

